title: Jungle_Initialisation
position: 36,-36
---
<<declare $Butterfly_Chase=0>>
<<set $Butterfly_Chase=0>>
===

title: Jungle_Main
position: 306,-32
---
<<detour JungleEnvironment>>
<<if $Random_Chance_Unlikely>>
    <<detour Jungle_Flavour>>
<<endif>>
<<jump Jungle_Main>>
===



title: JungleEnvironment
when: always
position: 1822,-29
---
You struggle through the undergrowth making slow but steady progress.
===
title: JungleEnvironment
when: always
position: 1619,-31
---
You follow a faint path for some time. 
=> Inhuman footprints are visible in the exposed earth. <<once if $Random_Chance_Likely==true>> 
=> You make rapid progress until it disappears into the underbrush 
    <<set $Adventure_Progress=$Adventure_Progress+2>>
=> The path ends at a sheer ravine - a collapsed bridge once crossed the path here
===
title: JungleEnvironment
when: always
position: 1411,-48
---
<<detour Challenge>>
===
title: JungleEnvironment
when: always
position: 1031,198
---
You walk out into a clearing. Sun peeks through the thick canopy illuminating the scene
===
title: JungleEnvironment
when: always
position: 1472,109
---
Thick undergrowth closes in on either side of the path forming a thin claustrophobic tunnel. You hurry through as fast as you can.
===
title: JungleEnvironment
when: always
position: 1487,-210
---
The view in front of you opens out into an awe inspiring sea of leaf and trees.
===
title: JungleEnvironment
when: always
position: 1224,122
---
You walk awhile along the banks of a wide river. Something stirs in the depths.
===
title: JungleEnvironment
when: $Random_Chance_Balanced==true
position: 1210,-213
---
The path opens out to reveal a beautiful crystal pool. The waters look cool and inviting
-> Swim a while
    <<if $Random_Chance_Unlikely>>
        Something stirs in the bottom of the pool and grabs at your legs. YOU struggle in vain as you are pulled under
        <<jump End>>
    <<else>>
        You take 10 minutes for a refreshing swim in the cool water. As you stride damply back into the jungle a strange splash comes from behind you. 
        <<return>>
    <<endif>>
->Carry on
    <<return>>
===
title: JungleEnvironment
when: $Butterfly_Chase > 3 and $Random_Chance_Balanced==true
position: 696,-37
---
Eyes still fully focused on the butterflies ahead you burst out of the undergrowth and over an unseen cliff. 
<<detour Cliff_Fall>>
===
title: JungleEnvironment
when:  $Random_Chance_Balanced==true
position: 25,-194
---
=>You come across an abandoned campsite under a large tree.
=>Set into a small cave in a nearby cliff you see an abandoned campfire. The area shows signs of a hasty exit with items strewn across the cliff mouth
=>Nestled into a small overhang in a nearby cliff you find the remains of a small camp
=>The clearing opens into a well organised camp
=>Perched in the low canopy of an enormous tree you see the remains of a camp
<<detour Camp_Main>>
===
