title: JungleEnvironment
when: $Random_Chance_Unlikely==true
position: 985,-40
---
Set into the cliff wall to your right is a dark entrance just wide enough for you to squeeze through sideways
-> Investigate
    You squeeze into the entrance, and tumble immediately into a larger cave. You are disoriented from your fall and can no longer see the entrance.
    <<detour Cave_Main>>
-> Carry on 
    You leave the caves for another day.
===

title: Jungle_Flavour
