---
The undergrowth ahead of you rustles as if something large and heavy is passing through. You decide not to investigate too closely.  
===
title: Jungle_Flavour
when: always
position: 842,658
---
=> A spray of rainbow butterflies rises from the Jungle floor and flies off to the north
=> Through the undergrowth in front of you a cloud of bright butterflies appears
->Follow them
    <<set $Butterfly_Chase=$Butterfly_Chase+1 >>
->Carry on
    You ignore them and follow your path forward
===
